  "texts": [
    "a Schematic of initial slide processing and grid preparation.",
    "Whole-slide images can be annotated with Regions of Interest (ROI) to include only relevant areas of a slide for subsequent analysis.",
    "Optional slide filtering steps, including Gaussian blur filtering and Otsu's thresholding, may be applied at this step.",
    "The remaining areas of the slide are sectioned into a grid in preparation for tile extraction.",
